Is the teacher using Activity Based Learning?
Are Learning Outcomes (Seekhne ke Pratifal) charts pasted in every classroom?
Are CCE records maintained?
Please ask atleast 3 students questions based on Learning Outcomes. How was their performance?
Does the school have access to clean drinking water?
Does the school have a functional library
Does the school need urgent safety repairs?
Has the school established functional science lab?
Does the school have electricity?
Are the toilets clean and functional?
Does the school have separate toilets for boys and girls?
Are ramps available in the school?
Are braille books available for visually challenged students?
Are all children sitting together without segregation on basis on caste, class, religion or physical or mental handicap?
No of unattended classrooms (i.e. teacher is not teaching in the classroom during class hours)
Is any teacher on unauthorised leave? If yes, then enter the name of teacher (For proof, take picture of attendance register)
No of Teacher Vacancies
Was SMC Meeting held in last month?
Are minutes of SMC meeting maintained?
Compared to last year, has there been increase or decrease in enrolment?
Is training for Out of School Children being done?
Are sports activities conducted?
Are co-curricular activities conducted?
Has the school filled its SDP? (online or offline)
Do the teachers watch TheTeacherApp courses suggested in Continuous Learning Programme?
Observation_Eng: They watch the courses but do not attend monthly Cluster Meetings for discussion
